7.   Type in <git add .>. - It will add all the files in the Folder for staging.\
8.   Type in <git commit -m \'93new commit\'94>. Or it maybe first commit, whatever you choose.  \
9.   Go to remote repo and copy the url (choose from SSH). \
10. Get back to terminal.\
